description:
By Canada's most read and recognized travel writer&nbsp;
First book with a personal review of the best northern experiences&nbsp;
Unlike traditional guidebooks, each chapter contains an inspirational story, placing each experience in context
Comprehensive online companion with practical information, video, galleries, reading guides, interactive polls, and contests&nbsp;
Supported by provincial marketing organizations, Parks Canada, and major Canadian brands&nbsp;
With thousands of followers, Robin has a strong social media presence across Facebook, Twitter and Instagram&nbsp;

A sought-after public speaker, Robin supports his books with speaking tours, and has been interviewed about his Bucket List on the CBC, CTV, Global, CityTV, <i>Canadian Living</i>, <i>Readers Digest</i>, <i>Canadian Traveller</i>, the <i>Globe and Mail</i>, and the <i>National Post</i>

